<p>Based upon Wally Lamb's 1998 novel: I Know This Much Is True also featured Melissa Leo, Juliette Lewis, Kathryn Hahn, and Rosie O'Donnell (R)</p>

<p>I Know This Much Is True - based upon Wally Lamb's 1998 novel - also featured Melissa Leo, Juliette Lewis, Kathryn Hahn, and Rosie O'Donnell.</p>

<p>Mark previously won Emmy gold for co-executive producing HBO series The Normal Heart in 2014.</p>

<p>When Ruffalo's name was called during the virtual ABC telecast, his wife Sunny jumped up and down four times and cried as they sat on the couch at their Sullivan County home in Upstate New York.</p>

